  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 2.3rem; font-weight: 700; color: #005181;">THE ANIMAL BUSINESS QUIZ – Extended Plan</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #333; max-width: 700px; margin: auto;">
      Dive deeper into your personalized 30-day domination strategy.
    </p>
